&lt;p&gt;There&amp;rsquo;s a manual:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="http://evalevanto.github.io/images/microcorruption/jakarta/jakarta-dets.png"&gt;&lt;img class="img" src="http://evalevanto.github.io/images/microcorruption/jakarta/jakarta-dets.png"
 alt/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passwords that are &lt;strong&gt;too long are rejected&lt;/strong&gt;. There is additional mechanisms to &lt;strong&gt;verify password length&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The lock is &lt;strong&gt;attached to&lt;/strong&gt; LockIT Pro &lt;strong&gt;HSM-1&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="http://evalevanto.github.io/images/microcorruption/jakarta/jakarta-hsm1.png"&gt;&lt;img class="img" src="http://evalevanto.github.io/images/microcorruption/jakarta/jakarta-hsm1.png"
 alt/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;main&lt;/code&gt; function just calls &lt;code&gt;login&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;login&lt;/code&gt; function is quite long:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="http://evalevanto.github.io/images/microcorruption/jakarta/jakarta-input-dets.png"&gt;&lt;img class="img" src="http://evalevanto.github.io/images/microcorruption/jakarta/jakarta-input-dets.png"
 alt/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="http://evalevanto.github.io/images/microcorruption/jakarta/jakarta-login-2.png"&gt;&lt;img class="img" src="http://evalevanto.github.io/images/microcorruption/jakarta/jakarta-login-2.png"
 alt/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="http://evalevanto.github.io/images/microcorruption/jakarta/jakarta-login-3.png"&gt;&lt;img class="img" src="http://evalevanto.github.io/images/microcorruption/jakarta/jakarta-login-3.png"
 alt/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Authentication requires a username and password input. The prompt states that these inputs together may &lt;strong&gt;not be more than 32 characters&lt;/strong&gt;. :D&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>